thread.title: Ed
thread.title_full: Official Car Mats reviewed by Ed

author: Ed
title: Ed
text:
I bought the top-level superior floor mats. I'd say they were the quality that I'd expect of a decent floor mats but nothing particularly superior to be honest.
They do fit, but the spacing around the accelerator pedal is a little odd. Very tight on one side, and an over-sized gap on the brake pedal side.
The mats are ok for the money.
